com.projetloki.genesis.image

Class Shape

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.projetloki.genesis.image.Shape
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Hashable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    TextShape, TextShape.Glyph

    public abstract class Shape
extends Object
implements Hashable
    A shape in the plane, defined by its interior.

    Shapes are immutable. All the methods transforming a shape, e.g. translate(double, double), return a new shape which is the result of the transformation and leave the original shape unmodified.

    All methods return serializable shapes as long as this and the arguments are serializable.
